Package: bayescm
Version: 0.0.0
Title: Bayesian Inference for Flexible Count Models
Description: Wrapper functions to Bayesian inference, based on MCMC, for
    flexible regression models, namely COM-Poisson and Gamma-Count.
    Under the hood, this package uses JAGS for MCMC sampling.
Authors@R: person(given = "Eduardo", family = "Ribeiro Jr",
                  email = "jreduardo@usp.br", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
SystemRequirements:
    JAGS 4.x.y
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
